  "title": "Customer Service Executive - Sea Freight [EL]",
  "description": "<ul>\n  <li>Support the sales department with daily operations and customer interactions.</li>\n  <li>Serve as the main point of coordination between customers, transporters, warehouses, and other stakeholders to ensure efficient logistics operations.</li>\n  <li>Prepare and manage all documentation related to imports, exports, transshipments, and delivery order (D/O) releases.</li>\n  <li>Verify shipment costs to ensure accuracy and compliance.</li>\n  <li>Address customer inquiries regarding rates, shipment tracking, and other logistics-related matters in a timely and professional manner.</li>\n  <li>Collaborate with overseas agents and customers to ensure smooth shipment handling and resolve any issues.</li>\n</ul>\n<p>We regret only shortlisted candidates will be contacted. All applications will be handled confidentially. By submitting your application, you agree to the collection, use, retention, and disclosure of your personal information to prospective employers.</p>\n<p><br></p>\n<p>Wecruit Pte Ltd</p>\n<p>EA License No: 20C0270</p>",
